Currently in the user profile section, the My Changes parameter has two options: Notify me and Do not notify me.  I have users that like to create issues using email and want to get an email back that contains the new issue number in the subject.  From my understanding, currently they must either use the UI or set their profile to notify them of all changes.  As a suggestion, it would be great to have a " on create issue only" setting.  I guess this would also have to work in conjunction with the project notification scheme as I assume having "Reporter" in the create issue section only works when the user creates from the UI.  Love the product, thank you for your consideration.

