For investigation purpose, I have attached two backup containing the same amount of data from 5.2.5 and also 6.2

Update: Since wiki rendering is supported on description field, it is affected as well

Given I am using the REST API to JIRA (EAC/J v6.2-rc1#6251-sha1:b1f5050)
And I have an issue that I want to do a workflow action to
When I send the transition request via REST:
{noformat}
POST http://localhost:2990/jira/rest/api/latest/issue/ODE-5/transitions 204
content-type=application/json
{
  "transition": {"id": 11},
  "update": {
    "comment": [{
      "add": {"body": "Go for DEV by Minion"}
    }]
  }
}
{noformat}
Then the request returns a success status
And the transition is done
But the comment does not appear on the issue
And no tracebacks appear in the log

